1.1.0.name: wordpress/oggchat-live-chat-software
1.1.0.description:
Interact directly with website visitors and increase sales with OggChat Live Chat. Chat with visitors from your IM or mobile phone. Just upload the plugin, enter your OggChat Chat Key, and immediately start offering live chat and live support on your website.

Why choose OggChat?

  • Simple Live Chat Installation

  • Chat right from your Instant Messenger - Gmail, Google Talk, iChat, iPhone, Android, BlackBerry

  • Monitor Website Visitors as they enter your website. Send proactive chat requests to them.

  • Customize the widget look and feel: Location, language, logos, default response messages

  • Select from Multiple Languages

To learn more about OggChat visit us at OggChat.com.
